Install:
- https://www.openshift.com/developers/rhc-client-tools-install
- rhc setup
- see credentials by mail

Application Name : ub
Domain : exanpe

Build:
- grails war -Dgrails.env=production

Information sources :
http://stackoverflow.com/questions/22675894/openshift-binary-deployment-tar-gz-structure

Upload:
- scp ROOT.war to app-root/data
- cp app-root/data/ROOT.war app-root/dependencies/jbossews/webapps/
- SSH ctl_all restart || rhc app-restart ub

External configuration :
- app-root/data/ub.properties

JBoss logs :
- rhc tail ub -o '-n 400' -f app-root/logs/jbossews.log

Access :
- application : http://ub-exanpe.rhcloud.com
- database (ko with firefox) : https://ub-exanpe.rhcloud.com/phpmyadmin/
